      ],
      "sub_groups": []
    },
    {
      "name": "In the R. V., “sheol” is translated “lowest pit” De 32:22; Ps 86:13",
      "references": [
        "Deut 32:22",
        "Ps 86:13"
      ],
      "sub_groups": []
    },
    {
      "name": "And it is translated “pit” in Ps 55:15",
